                            <comment id="14461323" author="phkim" created="Sun, 21 Aug 2005 22:23:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached file &quot;VarargsMethodTest.groovy&quot; is changed from your file so that it works.&lt;br/&gt;
